      • requestTrip

        public void requestTrip(Trip trip)
        Requests a Trip from the Dispatch. If the Dispatch finds a Driver, it will charge this Passenger. If the Passenger has enough money, the Driver will pick up the passenger. If the Driver search or financial transaction do not complete, this trip is cancelled and the appropriate information is logged.
        Parameters:
        trip - The Trip data for this trip
